data.title: Bob James
data.meta_description: Bob James. Soundtrack: The Big Hit. Bob James was born on 25 December 1939 in Marshall, Missouri, USA. He is a composer and actor, known for The Big Hit (1998), Doppelmord (1999) and Cop Out - Geladen und entsichert (2010). He has been married to Judy Heric since September 1963. They have one child.
